      "ja": "こんにちは、4人用のテーブルをお願いします。",
      "time": "00:00:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Of course, please follow me.",
      "zh": "當然，請跟我來。",
      "ja": "かしこまりました。こちらへどうぞ。",
      "time": "00:00:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Here's a table for four.",
      "zh": "這裡有一張四人桌。",
      "ja": "こちらが4人用のテーブルです。",
      "time": "00:00:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝。",
      "ja": "ありがとうございます。",
      "time": "00:00:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Could you give us the menu please?",
      "zh": "可以給我們菜單嗎？",
      "ja": "メニューをいただけますか？",
      "time": "00:00:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes, of course.",
      "zh": "好的，當然。",
      "ja": "はい、もちろんです。",
      "time": "00:00:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝。",
      "ja": "ありがとうございます。",
      "time": "00:00:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Can I get you anything to drink?",
      "zh": "要喝點什麼嗎？",
      "ja": "お飲み物はいかがですか？",
      "time": "00:00:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Just water for me.",
      "zh": "我只要水。",
      "ja": "私は水だけでいいです。",
      "time": "00:00:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'll have a lemonade.",
      "zh": "我要檸檬水。",
      "ja": "レモネードをください。",
      "time": "00:00:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'll have a little shake.",
      "zh": "我要一杯奶昔。",
      "ja": "シェイクをお願いします。",
      "time": "00:00:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I have an orange juice.",
      "zh": "我要一杯柳橙汁。",
      "ja": "オレンジジュースをください。",
      "time": "00:00:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Great.",
      "zh": "很好。",
      "ja": "いいですね。",
      "time": "00:00:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'll be right back.",
      "zh": "我馬上回來。",
      "ja": "すぐ戻ります。",
      "time": "00:00:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Are you ready to order?",
      "zh": "準備好點餐了嗎？",
      "ja": "ご注文はお決まりですか？",
      "time": "00:00:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes, we are.",
      "zh": "是的，我們準備好了。",
      "ja": "はい、決まりました。",
      "time": "00:00:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'll have the grilled chicken and a salad.",
      "zh": "我要烤雞和沙拉。",
      "ja": "グリルチキンとサラダをお願いします。",
      "time": "00:00:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Would you like a starter?",
      "zh": "要不要先來個前菜？",
      "ja": "前菜はいかがですか？",
      "time": "00:01:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes, I'd like the vegetable soup.",
      "zh": "好的，我想要蔬菜湯。",
      "ja": "はい、野菜スープをお願いします。",
      "time": "00:01:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "For the main course, I'd like the grilled fish.",
      "zh": "主菜我要烤魚。",
      "ja": "メインはグリルフィッシュをお願いします。",
      "time": "00:01:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'll have the chicken soup and the lasagna.",
      "zh": "我要雞湯和千層麵。",
      "ja": "チキンスープとラザニアをお願いします。",
      "time": "00:01:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'll have the chicken soup, the grilled chicken and some salad.",
      "zh": "我要雞湯、烤雞和一些沙拉。",
      "ja": "チキンスープ、グリルチキン、サラダをお願いします。",
      "time": "00:01:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Excellent.",
      "zh": "太好了。",
      "ja": "素晴らしいです。",
      "time": "00:01:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'll be right back.",
      "zh": "我馬上回來。",
      "ja": "すぐ戻ります。",
      "time": "00:01:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mmm, it's not so great.",
      "zh": "嗯，這不太好吃。",
      "ja": "うーん、あまり美味しくない。",
      "time": "00:01:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm so hungry and I want to eat, but the soup is so hot.",
      "zh": "我很餓想吃，但湯太燙了。",
      "ja": "お腹が空いていて食べたいけど、スープが熱すぎる。",
      "time": "00:01:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I can barely touch it.",
      "zh": "我幾乎碰不了它。",
      "ja": "ほとんど触れません。",
      "time": "00:01:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Wait for it to cool down before you eat it.",
      "zh": "等它涼一點再吃。",
      "ja": "冷めるまで待ってから食べてください。",
      "time": "00:01:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The grilled chicken tastes delicious.",
      "zh": "烤雞味道很好。",
      "ja": "グリルチキンは美味しいです。",
      "time": "00:01:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Doesn't it, Paul?",
      "zh": "是吧，保羅？",
      "ja": "そうでしょう、ポール？",
      "time": "00:01:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes, Dad.",
      "zh": "是的，爸爸。",
      "ja": "はい、お父さん。",
      "time": "00:01:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It doesn't eat.",
      "zh": "它不吃。",
      "ja": "それは食べません。",
      "time": "00:01:39"
