      "time": "00:01:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I love it.",
      "zh": "我喜歡它。",
      "ja": "大好きです。",
      "time": "00:01:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's my favorite dish.",
      "zh": "這是我最喜歡的菜。",
      "ja": "私のお気に入りの料理です。",
      "time": "00:01:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Great.",
      "zh": "太好了。",
      "ja": "素晴らしい。",
      "time": "00:01:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "How's your dish, Mom?",
      "zh": "妳的菜怎麼樣，媽媽？",
      "ja": "お母さん、料理はどうですか？",
      "time": "00:01:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's excellent.",
      "zh": "非常好吃。",
      "ja": "とても美味しいです。",
