      "time": "00:02:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes, it was wonderful.",
      "zh": "是的，非常棒。",
      "ja": "はい、とても素晴らしかったです。",
      "time": "00:02:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you.",
