      "time": "00:04:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I like it spicy and salty.",
      "zh": "我喜歡辣又鹹的味道。",
      "ja": "辛くて塩辛い味が好きです。",
      "time": "00:04:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "So do you often eat fast food?",
      "zh": "那你經常吃速食嗎？",
